{"tid":391681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我咁樣係有情緒病定太愛佢","createTime":"2017-09-08T03:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T15:23:37.000Z","uid":143191,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b3748a3e0378c1fdc1002b5ff56671fa5ead77","tid":391681,"uid":143191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊咗一個月<br />\n自認係一個好痴身既女仔<br />\n成日會好掛住男朋友<br />\n我平時已經有安排下節目俾自己<br />\n有約fd有返pt<br />\n我明白我既世界唔係淨係得佢<br />\n問題黎啦<br />\n9月開sem好忙<br />\n冇得日日搵<br />\n依架每次諗起佢都會好心up<br />\n係up到喊嗰隻<br />\n但又唔可以搵佢同佢講<br />\n唔想俾太大壓力同太chur佢<br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣<br />\n俾啲方法我cool down下<br />\n等我唔好掛住佢掛到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4439f874b3b3adf3c25528b23e770648b299bb00","tid":391681,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:22:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afee11532e9ea24427702bf9115de2677145c96c","tid":391681,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:22:48.000Z","msg":"有病"},{"pid":"3c11d235b38bd523b311d07e56211c749d94815f","tid":391681,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"好chur啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8512eacfa5e2191478d8fa34a738cafad562334a","tid":391681,"uid":72445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"第一次拍拖？"},{"pid":"d3ccd46ac590544e9d7542d10ccda4990f906335","tid":391681,"uid":125589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"未去到喊嘅 不過都會好掛住 大家一星期訂一兩日見 咁你其餘嘅日子就可以專心做自己嘢"},{"pid":"27b05acfd3fca8bd60d74c84d0118944dfb5fa8f","tid":391681,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"有病"},{"pid":"a9ad6b6764f4ef104d70677338d123b82f8ebc38","tid":391681,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0